---

<section class="manifesto">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="manifesto-inner">
      <div class="manifesto-bg-text" aria-hidden="true">MANIFESTO</div>

      <div class="manifesto-content">
        <div class="manifesto-label">cat engineer_manifesto.md</div>

        <h2 class="manifesto-heading">PLATFORM AS A<br />FORCE MULTIPLIER</h2>

        <div class="manifesto-body">
          <p>
            "The platform's job is to disappear. When developers ship without thinking about
            infrastructure, the platform has done its job. Every manual step, every tribal
            knowledge dependency, every ticket to the platform team — is a bug."
          </p>
          <p>
            "Complexity is the enemy of reliability. We don't add observability after the fact.
            We don't bolt on security. We don't optimize after the outage. We build it in from
            the start, or we accept the consequences."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="manifesto-principles">
          <p>1. Automate or it will bite you at 3am.</p>
          <p>2. GitOps over ClickOps — if it's not in git, it doesn't exist.</p>
          <p>3. Observability over intuition. Alert on symptoms, not causes.</p>
          <p>4. Developer experience is platform correctness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto {
    padding: 64px 0;
  }

  .manifesto-inner {
    background: var(--bg-low);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
    padding: 48px 56px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .manifesto-bg-text {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    padding: 16px;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text);
    opacity: 0.03;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .manifesto-content {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .manifesto-label {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--secondary);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .manifesto-heading {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .manifesto-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-style: italic;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--border);
    padding-left: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .manifesto-body p {
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .manifesto-principles {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .manifesto-inner { padding: 32px 24px; }
  }
</style>
